node.text:
This is truly a must-listen.

I’m crying right now listening to this phone call. It hit me like a freight train, I can feel her pain and anger all at the same time. 

20 yr old Rylee McCollum was one of the 13 Marines killed in the suicide bombing in Kabul.

His mom called into the Wilkow Majority Show on Sirius XM Channel 125. This is truly a must-listen.✅

Her representative @repboebert has reached out & is visiting her home. The White House has not.

May be an image of outdoors and text that says '海 Daily Mail NEWS The Taliban say they are 'angry and disappointed' and feel 'betrayed' after America left so many inoperable helicopters and planes because 'the aircraft belong to Afghanistan''.

node.text:
An Al Jazeera journalist reported that the Taliban are disappointed, they are angry, they feel betrayed because all of this equipment is broken beyond repair.'

US troops 'demilitarised' 73 aircraft in Kabul, Airport before their departure this week according to the commander of the US evacuation mission, Gen. Frank McKenzie.

That left up to 48 aircraft in the hands of the terror group, although it was not known how many were operable.

But the Taliban had 'expected the Americans to leave helicopters in one piece for their use', according to an Al Jazeera reporter who toured the airport after the withdrawal.

She said: 'When I said to them, "why do you think that the Americans would have left everything operational for you?" They said because we believe it is a national asset and we are the government now and this could have come to great use for us.'

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Latinos With Trump on September 02, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'BREITBART NEWS Exclusive 一 Oliver North: Weapons, Equipment Abandoned in Afghanistan Will Be 'Reverse- Reverse-Engineered in China, 'Used Against Us''.

node.text:
The Joe Biden administration left behind “some of the most sophisticated weapons and equipment we’ve ever made for the military,” Ret. Lt. Col. Oliver North stated. He warned, “It’s going to be reverse-engineered in China. It will be reverse-engineered in Russia. It will be used against us in other campaigns.”

“Now, other people will be using our weapons to shoot at us,” he concluded. “We’re going to see a lot of that weaponry used against us in a lot of places.”

Biden continually chafed at suggestions US troops should remain in Afghanistan for much longer, according to people familiar with the matter, reminding his advisers that -- like his two predecessors -- he promised voters he would end the country's longest war, even if that meant going against the recommendations of his top generals.

"Don't underestimate Joe's ability to f-u-c-k things up." ~ Barack Obama

Joe Biden made the world an unsafe place just so that he could keep a campaign promise ignoring his top military commanders

node.text:
Whether it was classified or not classified, answer the question. America now knows of the catastrophic failures at the Pentagon for allowing 13 US Service members to be murdered. 

They KNEW! They had advance notice the suicide bombing was going to occur at Kabul Airport and could have avoided last week’s airport bombing that killed 13 US service members, according to leaked information obtained by Politico. 

Can we really trust the Biden Administration to conduct an investigation into their own failures? It’s like asking a murderer to be the judge and jury at their own murder trial. 

“The transcript of three conference calls, authenticated by a defense official, details conversations among the highest levels of Pentagon leadership. It makes clear that top officials were raising alarm bells and preparing for a potential attack that they had narrowed down to a handful of possible targets and a 24-48 hour time frame — projections that ended up being deadly accurate.” ~ POLITICO 
.
.
.

The Taliban Commander told RT News Correspondents about the dogs on camera. (Seen here)

Off camera: that they would put them to use, and that they would train those they could source ~ 

This statement by the Taliban contradicted what the Joe Biden administration said that the dogs were stray dogs.. What we are seeing and hearing is quite the opposite of what the Biden Administration is saying. These Dogs look like German Shepherds and Belgian Malinois MWD’s/ CWD’s and not stray dogs.

node.text:
*Update The latest on the abandoned K9 Dogs left behind in Afghanistan as of 9/1/21 

“The Taliban’s commander of Kabul airport tells us US troops let their service dogs free as they evacuated.

The dogs are being rounded up, and the Taliban plans to, in an ironic twist, put them back into service for the Islamic Emirate.

(No, they weren’t sentenced to death)” ~ @rt ~ Correspondent Murad Gazdiev 

[unconfirmed reports say 50 of them are CWDs - highly trained working dogs who worked with U.S. and coalition forces] 

[MWDs (Military Working Dog) and CWDs (Contractor Working Dog) work alongside one another protecting both US and Coalition Forces in all areas. They bring life-saving capability to the fight against Terrorism regardless of the initials (MWD or CWD) which precede their names.]

POWERFUL WORDS from Shanna Chappel, the mother of Lance Cpl. Kareem Nikoui, who had her Facebook and Instagram accounts taken down due to her posts which contained some harsh comments about President Joe Biden. [SEE SLIDE 2]✅

President Trump responded to her post [SLIDE 1]✅

These parents are dealing with the loss of their sons and daughters, and anger is part of the grieving process. It would not be unheard of to blame the commander in chief for losing a loved one while in military service, but there is a consensus from many of the families that there was disrespect done to them and their soldiers by Joe Biden at the ceremony.

I’ll just leave this right here! Don’t get me started. I’m glad someone said it out loud, but I’m so sorry the reason that makes this mother qualified to be heard is devastating.

And where the F~u~c~k is @kamalaharris @vp , as much as I don’t like the woman she would probably have done a better job at listening to the families who lost their sons and daughters. This old POS 💩 has to go. #impeachbiden and #removebiden
